## Full Version

The full version of this project, including:
- Core generator code (karaoke_alignment_generator.py)
- Mobile generator code (karaoke_mobile_generator.py)
- Batch processing tools (50-100 videos per day capability)
- Advanced features and configurations

is currently in development.

NOTE: Story content (text and audio files) is NOT included in the open source release.
Users need to prepare their own English text and audio files.

### Open Source Commitment

When this project reaches the following goal, the full version will be 
released under the MIT License and become completely open source:

- 2,000 sponsors AND total amount of ¥20,000
- OR total amount reaches ¥20,000 (regardless of sponsor count)

Minimum sponsorship: ¥10 / $1.5 per sponsor

Current Progress: 0 / 2,000 sponsors, ¥0 / ¥20,000

For sponsorship information, see: SPONSORSHIP.md

